OL,3,CBirmingham City footballer Marvin
OL,4,CDucksch charged with drink driving
OL,6,FA Birmingham City footballer has been
OL,7,Fcharged with drink driving after a
OL,8,Fcrash involving three cars near Henley-
OL,9,Fin-Arden in Warwickshire.
OL,11,FWarwickshire Police confirmed that a
OL,12,F32-year-old man has been charged after
OL,13,Fofficers attended reports of a
OL,14,Fcollision on the A3400 on Monday 6
OL,15,FApril at around 10:30pm.
OL,17,FThe crash happened close to where the
OL,18,Fclub's training ground is based.
