OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776341451
OL,3,CBirmingham City footballer Marvin
OL,4,CDucksch charged with drink driving
OL,6,FMarvin Ducksch was arrested yesterday
OL,7,F(13 April) and has been bailed to
OL,8,Fappear before Warwickshire Magistrates
OL,9,FCourt in Leamington on Wednesday 20
OL,10,FMay.
OL,12,FBirmingham City has acknowledged the
OL,13,Fincident and says they are dealing
OL,14,Fwith the matter internally.
OL,16,FEarlier on the day of the alleged
OL,17,Fincident, Ducksch played in
OL,18,FBirmingham's 2-1 defeat to Ipswich
OL,19,FTown away at Portman Road.
